page.title: 01Our D Block
page.content: Our D block is 4km by 3km.It starts at Crediton Station and finishes at Newton St. Cyces Station.There is a small branch line running from/to{ {BARNSTABLE,CREDITON,NEWTON ST. {CYRES,EXETER ST. DAVIDS}through our bottom 4 blocks.We have the A377 running through 3 squares.Our block is mostly made up of farm and grazing land. There is Shobrooke Park in a square and next to that in our other square there is a village called Shobrooke.There are alot of rivers and farms around the place.We have two major squares,one with the industrial estate and another with the station,light industres and garages. The whole sqare is full of rolling hills,wildlife and lots of country side.Its a loverly place to be.
